<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <title>AI活用度診断 | RAKUDA AI SOLUTION</title>
  <meta name="description" content="3分で御社のAI活用ポテンシャルがわかる無料診断ツール。10問の質問に回答するだけで、AI導入による効率化の可能性を即座にスコアリング。">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    /* ── Diagnostic Tool Styles ─────────────────────────── */
    .diag-hero {
      padding: 64px 24px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light) 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
    }
    .diag-hero-inner {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .diag-hero h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .diag-hero h1 span { color: var(--primary); }
    .diag-hero p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* Progress */
    .diag-progress-bar {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }
    .diag-progress-track {
      height: 6px;
      background: var(--border);
      border-radius: 3px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .diag-progress-track .progress-fill {
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--primary);
      border-radius: 3px;
      transition: width 0.4s ease;
      width: 0;
    }
    .diag-progress-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* Question area */
    .diag-container {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 32px auto 80px;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .diag-question-card {
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .diag-question-number {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    .diag-question-text {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    /* Options as cards */
    .diag-options {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .diag-option {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: left;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background: var(--bg);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.15s;
      font-family: inherit;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .diag-option:hover {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      background: var(--primary-light);
    }
    .diag-option.is-selected {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      background: var(--primary-light);
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Navigation */
    .diag-nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .diag-btn {
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.15s;
      border: none;
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    .diag-btn:disabled {
      opacity: 0.4;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }
    .diag-btn--prev {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .diag-btn--prev:hover:not(:disabled) {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .diag-btn--next, .diag-btn--submit, .diag-btn--primary {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #FFF;
    }
    .diag-btn--next:hover:not(:disabled),
    .diag-btn--submit:hover:not(:disabled),
    .diag-btn--primary:hover:not(:disabled) {
      background: var(--primary-dark);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .diag-btn--secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .diag-btn--secondary:hover {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .diag-btn--outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .diag-btn--outline:hover {
      border-color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    /* Email step */
    .diag-email-step {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px;
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .diag-email-step h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .diag-email-step p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .diag-email-form {
      max-width: 360px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
    }
    .diag-input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-family: inherit;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .diag-input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(30,58,95,0.1);
    }

    /* Results */
    .diag-results {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .diag-score-section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .diag-score-circle {
      position: relative;
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
      margin: 0 auto 16px;
    }
    .diag-score-svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      transform: rotate(-90deg);
    }
    .diag-score-bg {
      fill: none;
      stroke: var(--border);
      stroke-width: 8;
    }
    .diag-score-fill {
      fill: none;
      stroke-width: 8;
      stroke-linecap: round;
      transition: stroke-dasharray 1.5s ease-out;
    }
    .diag-score-value {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .diag-score-number {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .diag-score-unit {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
    .diag-level-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 20px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      color: #FFF;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    /* Recommendations */
    .diag-recommendations {
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .diag-recommendations h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .diag-rec-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .diag-rec-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: var(--bg-alt);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .diag-rec-number {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #FFF;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .diag-rec-content h4 {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .diag-rec-content p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* CTA */
    .diag-cta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    /* Error */
    .diag-error {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .diag-error p {
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .diag-hero h1 { font-size: 24px; }
      .diag-question-card { padding: 24px; }
      .diag-score-circle { width: 140px; height: 140px; }
      .diag-cta { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
      .diag-cta .diag-btn { width: 100%; text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="diag-hero">
  <div class="diag-hero-inner">
    <h1><span>AI活用度診断</span><br>3分で御社のAI活用ポテンシャルがわかる</h1>
    <p>10問の簡単な質問に回答するだけで、御社の業務におけるAI活用の可能性をスコアリング。業界別ベンチマークとの比較レポートを即時発行します。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Progress bar -->
<div class="diag-progress-bar">
  <div id="diagProgress" class="diag-progress-track">
    <div class="progress-fill"></div>
  </div>
  <div id="diagProgressText" class="diag-progress-text">0 / 10 回答済み</div>
</div>

<!-- Question Area -->
<div class="diag-container">
  <div id="diagQuestionArea">
    <div style="text-align:center;padding:40px;color:var(--text-sub);">
      質問を読み込み中...
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
<%- include('../partials/contact-modal') %>
<%- include('../partials/booking-modal') %>
<%- include('../partials/chatbot') %>

<script src="/js/tracking.js"></script>
<script src="/js/contact.js"></script>
<script src="/js/booking.js"></script>
<script src="/js/chatbot.js"></script>
<script src="/js/diagnostic.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
